Recommends: rpicam-hello | libcamera-hello
Description: Raspberry Pi camera utilities (camview)
 picam provides camview, a Cheese-like preview and capture tool for Raspberry Pi 5
 CSI/MIPI cameras using GStreamer and libcamera. It supports graphical preview,
 headless still capture, and timed H.264 recording. The package also builds the
 small shared libpicam library used by the project.
